reviewText: Disc is no good, does not play at all. I tried it in 3 different players, zilch.
Haven't seen it yet; but, I'm sure it will be interesting.

I bought this DVD hoping to learn a lot more about Audie Murphy.  BIG DISAPPOINTMENT!  Only at the very end is there a short PSA featuring Audie selling War Bonds.  Save your money if you're wanting a healthy dose of Audie.  It's a Newsreel of WWII, which you can probably watch on YouTube.
